		"description": "<p>Also at 1st level you gain a special ability tied to the experiments that were pressed upon you. Your bonded power must be of the same line as your flesh and bone selection.</p>\n<p><strong>Beastmantle</strong>: You gain a Bite attack as a natural weapon which deals 1d6+Str piercing damage. When you cast a spell with a range of touch you may use your bite attack as part of the spellcasting action to deliver the spell. In addition you grow a long tail with a stinger. As a bonus action on your turn you may use your tail as a natural finesse weapon to attack. On a hit you deal 1d4 piercing damage and poison damage equal to your Constitution modifier.</p>",
